        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "Add ClawHub skill verification and trust surfaces",
        "body": "## Summary\n- adds `openclaw skills verify <slug>` backed by ClawHub `/verify`, with `--version`, `--tag`, `--card`, shared/global workspace, and installed/uninstalled target resolution\n- resolves installed ClawHub skills from installer-owned lock/origin metadata and fails closed on malformed trust envelopes/card downloads\n- adds `skills.securityVerdicts` and `skills.skillCard` gateway methods so Control UI can show a top-level ClawHub verdict plus a lazy local `skill-card.md` tab\n- keeps verdict fetching bulk/narrow: one passive unauthenticated request for linked installs, no card data and no full scanner payload; detailed reports link out to ClawHub\n\n## Cross-repo dependency\n- depends on ClawHub bulk verdict endpoint in openclaw/clawhub#2404: `POST /api/v1/skills/-/security-verdicts`\n- OpenClaw intentionally does not fall back to N per-skill requests; pre-deploy/old ClawHub endpoints can report verdicts unavailable until the ClawHub PR ships\n\n## Linear\n- CLAW-179 root\n- CLAW-180, CLAW-181, CLAW-182, CLAW-183, CLAW-184\n- CLAW-190, CLAW-191, CLAW-192, CLAW-193\n- CLAW-186 tracks the ClawHub CLI cleanup to remove its redundant `--json` flag\n\n## Tests\n- `CI=true pnpm test src/infra/clawhub.test.ts src/agents/skills-clawhub.test.ts src/cli/skills-cli.commands.test.ts src/cli/skills-cli.verify.test.ts -- --reporter=dot`\n- `CI=true pnpm check:changed`\n- `CI=true pnpm format:docs:check`\n- `git diff --check`\n- `pnpm test src/agents/skills-status.test.ts src/gateway/server-methods/skills.clawhub.test.ts src/infra/clawhub.test.ts src/gateway/server-methods-list.test.ts ui/src/ui/controllers/skills.test.ts ui/src/ui/views/skills.test.ts`\n- `pnpm tsgo:core`\n- `pnpm tsgo:test:src`\n- `pnpm tsgo:test:ui`\n- `pnpm check:changed`\n- `pnpm ui:build`\n- `pnpm protocol:check`\n- `pnpm ui:i18n:check`\n\n## UI proof\nSkills list verdict:\n\n![Skills list verdict](https://uploads.linear.app/f62397ba-7118-4506-b4a8-119d64e590a4/85031632-42a3-4397-bc43-038a8e25ae04/f6ccf001-8a5b-4312-922e-400244e61501)\n\nVerdict overview and full-report link:\n\n![Verdict overview](https://uploads.linear.app/f62397ba-7118-4506-b4a8-119d64e590a4/60c1126e-248b-4de9-b1cb-f881abb94a9b/29131f94-67d2-4b28-9cd0-7c119bf0e632)\n\nLocal Skill Card tab:\n\n![Skill Card tab](https://uploads.linear.app/f62397ba-7118-4506-b4a8-119d64e590a4/c1c30c79-dc1a-4dee-92ab-6f8c2d874ebb/d950efc8-55ea-4a33-9075-9cc4d6a41018)\n\nLocal screenshot copies:\n- skills list: `/tmp/openclaw-claw-192-skills-list.png`\n- verdict overview: `/tmp/openclaw-claw-192-verdict-overview.png`\n- skill card tab: `/tmp/openclaw-claw-192-skill-card-tab.png`\n\n## Review\n- autoreview accepted findings fixed: verified card URL binding, missing card metadata, card byte cap, release-owned changelog removal, fail-closed malformed decisions, lockfile-corroborated installed origin metadata, method reachability, token-safe passive verdict fetches, lazy/symlink-safe local card reads, provenance install-dir/registry checks, non-blocking verdict refresh, and stale Skill Card cache guards\n- final read-only subagent review: no blocking findings after fixes\n- final autoreview remaining finding rejected as an expected cross-repo dependency on openclaw/clawhub#2404, verified in that ClawHub branch\n",
